869928225.text: "In our current study, the combination of mitomycin C and rapamycin inactivated not only Akt but also S6K1, led to dephosphorylated Bad, and resulted in dissociation of Bcl-xL from pro apoptotic protein Bak, inducing mitochondria dependent apoptosis."
